Alcatel discusses Thomson bid with Aerospatiale , Dassault . Alcatel Alsthom on Monday said it was in talks with state - owned Aerospatiale and Dassault Aviation about a possible joint offer for the state ' s majority stake in Thomson - CSF . " There are discussions with the companies mentioned in the press , " a company spokesman said . Earlier on Monday , Prime Minister Alain Juppe said a decision about the sale of Thomson - CSF would be made before the end of February . 
